# World of Movies

Final semester project at CSU Stanislaus developed by Bryan Denman, Jay, and Susana.

**World of Movies** is a web-based application built with PHP, MySQL, and HTML that allows users to explore movies, actors, directors, genres, filming locations, awards, and related information.

### Features

* Relational database schema connecting movies, actors, directors, producers, awards, and more.
* Interactive queries to search movie data by cast, reviews, production details, awards, and directors.
* Ad-hoc query interface to allow users to run custom SQL queries on movie and actor tables.
* Web pages dynamically generated using PHP and MySQL for seamless interaction.

This project showcases database design, backend integration, and front-end presentation as part of the Computer Science program at CSU Stanislaus.
